## ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack

We selected this stack for its performance, developer experience, and cost-efficiency (free tier friendly):

-   **[Astro](https://astro.build)**: The web framework. Optimized for static content and speed.
-   **[Tailwind CSS](https://tailwindcss.com)**: A utility-first CSS framework for rapid UI development.
-   **[Keystatic](https://keystatic.com)**: A Git-based Content Management System (CMS). No database required.
-   **[Netlify](https://netlify.com)**: Hosting platform and serverless backend functions.
-   **[Google Gmail API](https://developers.google.com/gmail/api)**: For sending emails securely via OAuth2 / backend.
-   **[Cloudflare Turnstile](https://www.cloudflare.com/products/turnstile/)**: Privacy-focused CAPTCHA alternative to block spam.

